  m_text: Hi, um, me and my roommate have been hearing his dog outside our dorm.
    Admin told us not to worry about it, but it's getting louder. I think I've also
    heard my sister. Last time I called, the lady told me not to worry, yet there's
    a sound that just keeps getting closer to the dorm. It sounds like someone's
    lugging a dead body, and it's making us go insane. Please help.
